{"tid":2041993,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[jj插沙求救][多圖]執左隻受傷流浪貓","createTime":"2020-05-29T14:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T03:46:07.000Z","uid":3627,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2e7bb44a954a5df44762cc8a12c58a6110b6df","tid":2041993,"uid":3627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"我係爆武漢肺炎之前過左去泰國。然後係住既地方附近遇到隻流浪貓，係貓女黎既。而家佢既右手+左腳受左傷。佢既右手痛到企係度同坐係度都拎起隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢隻右手好似有傷口，唔知有冇腫左<br />\n<br />\n而家雨季外面會突然橫風橫雨，我見佢太可憐就執左佢返去....但係我完全冇養貓經驗，而且都未知邊度有講英文既獸醫睇。<br />\n<br />\n所以想問全能既連登仔，係睇獸醫之前我有啲咩野可以為佢做，有咩方法可以幫到隻貓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bys5DZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBys5DZm.jpg&h=f9229cea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eH1x3rx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeH1x3rx.jpg&h=530786ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qd4ci0r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQd4ci0r.jpg&h=125faa3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j42xi06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj42xi06.jpg&h=3006c86c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggDP5G4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggDP5G4.jpg&h=b15b66a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0CJqHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0CJqHJ.jpg&h=c135b131&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZ5Cvae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZ5Cvae.jpg&h=1b01830c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rraQaL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rraQaL.jpg&h=07bb4f18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xz2xi4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxz2xi4O.jpg&h=1e427601&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2y4UDP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2y4UDP.jpg&h=40e7b859&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3ujJyX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3ujJyX.jpg&h=4278ad07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7g5nGmv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7g5nGmv.jpg&h=dd7898bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c684bd94e195cd2e719fb004c8a9bf99118808c3","tid":2041993,"uid":69309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"推先"},{"pid":"ad1240c5e1caca07972372fb219176fb3e212411","tid":2041993,"uid":3627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"而家佢行步路都好辛苦咁拐下拐下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n胃口同精神比琴日差左少少<br />\n但都仲肯行路同埋跳黎跳去，仲跳上張檯度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f915ffd5ca50b968d826b5c437fee347a09ab0a","tid":2041993,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:49:42.000Z","msg":"唔識<br />\n但幫推"},{"pid":"c965aecf6cd9f3cdfeb69b360c29071cebf1faea","tid":2041993,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7be6540bd1def5be83d9c900aaad9b90bd83360","tid":2041993,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"e生"},{"pid":"9cdbd420f98682f00350990c0d01f0d6e3f1550c","tid":2041993,"uid":12251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"點解隻手咁短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76f8328ecd6207766e63e496da17a9f0afc3b86","tid":2041993,"uid":331169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"794669a5e340c32802dfc5a71207c1e42558